data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLER** This home has EVERYTHING you are looking for sitting on 1.5 acres in ALEDO ISD. Very unique lot with 2 driveways and tons of extra space for parking an RV, extra cars or a potential guest home. Recently remodeled kitchen with double convection ovens, matching GE profile appliances, cabinet slide outs with double lazy Susans & soft close design. Hardwood floors throughout. Brand new pool, barely 6 months old, with tanning pad, swim up ledge, diving rock, weeping waterfall, brand new pool pump with UV filter. Custom gate around pool, patio with self latching locks for safety. Renovated master bath with jacuzzi soaking tub. Brand new hot water heater. HUGE shop with electric.
